      <title>Vista 首次进军非洲以外市场，将银行业务拓展至法国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/vista-expands-banking-to-france-in-first-outside-africa-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vista Group 收购了法国兴业银行和法国巴黎银行的非洲业务，目前正将业务拓展至法国，因为这家总部位于布基纳法索的银行希望挖掘非洲和欧洲之间的贸易机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/vista-expands-banking-to-france-in-first-outside-africa-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 05:43:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
